{"tid":2495890,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[ViuTV] [19:30-20:00] 囝囝女女730 (7) 永續全民造星3","createTime":"2021-04-19T12:39:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T11:45:35.000Z","uid":14788,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4d0bff9b32d3eab6966fac7f5250cd30290b3c64","tid":2495890,"uid":14788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:39:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=9emug-44lO4&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9emug-44lO4%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=5a6f02b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=9emug-44lO4&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n【2021綜藝新時段！《囝囝女女730》即將首播🌟】<br />\n<br />\n新一年，除咗可以繼續重溫《全民造星III》嘅經典畫面，仲有新福利🥳🥳<br />\n我哋延續造星嘅青春同熱血，推出屬於香港年輕人嘅綜藝節目《囝囝女女730》！由今季造星參賽者拍住大師兄MIRROR，加埋老是常出現嘅宇宙級壓台之寶「全尼 (2021 version）」 ，仲有養眼孖寶Shirley同Angie！<br />\n<br />\n晚晚唔同主持，唔同嘉賓，瘋狂battle兼爆料，誓要炸爆個場，睇到你欲罷不能！<br />\n想知夜晚7:30可以玩到有幾癲？下星期一晚，一齊睇首播啦！<br />\n<br />\n《#囝囝女女730》1月18日起 逢星期一至五晚上 7:30<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每晚唔同主題：<br />\n<br />\n星期一：全能強尼帶領歌手們互爆樂壇秘密！（有大量靚聲福利）<br />\n星期二：Shirley同Angie約埋造星女女大爆少女心事！<br />\n星期三：Lokman、Tiger聯同造星囝女，集氣煉成全能藝人！<br />\n星期四：Alton、Frankie拍住上，call埋造星囝囝狂吹男人經！<br />\n星期五：花癡女神阿正，召喚造星界文青齊齊氣質level up！"},{"pid":"a9082e5a3ebb3f7ffbede7ac5f2dd6db8911057f","tid":2495890,"uid":313584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:54:25.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"c0ef5598caadb8b0493d3d9f5017f0c17f3f4703","tid":2495890,"uid":173032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:39:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>"},{"pid":"a2a7cf412cbef6b55b07d2a064301bae77f13acb","tid":2495890,"uid":231622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T17:32:19.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"5235eed